<refsect1>
<title>Description</title>

<para>
The <link linkend="GtkHScrollbar"><type>GtkHScrollbar</type></link> widget is a widget arranged horizontally creating a
scrollbar. See <link linkend="GtkScrollbar"><type>GtkScrollbar</type></link> for details on
scrollbars. <link linkend="GtkAdjustment"><type>GtkAdjustment</type></link> pointers may be added to handle the
adjustment of the scrollbar or it may be left <literal>NULL</literal> in which case one
will be created for you. See <link linkend="GtkAdjustment"><type>GtkAdjustment</type></link> for details.
</para>
</refsect1>

